query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 t1 tq1 s) NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoMergeJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('banach-spaces',
'contour-integration',
'generating-functions',
'group-theory')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Autobiographer',
'Commentator',
'Critic',
'Enlightened',
'Good Answer',
'Informed',
'Nice Answer',
'Nice Question',
'Notable Question',
'Organizer',
'Popular Question',
'Supporter',
'Teacher',
'Yearling')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
